          <text><![CDATA[<p> Authorizes the Department of Veterans Affairs (VA) to issue an order directing a VA employee to repay the amount, or a portion of the amount, of an award or bonus paid to the employee if: (1) the VA determines that such repayment is appropriate, and (2) the employee is afforded notice and an opportunity for a hearing conducted by another federal agency. Makes such repayment decisions final and unreviewable.</p> <p>Makes this Act applicable to awards or bonuses paid before, on, or after the date of this Act's enactment.</p>]]></text>
